articles.title: Tropical Storm Sara forms in the Caribbean and heads toward ‘life-threatening’ impact with Central America - CNN
articles.description: The National Hurricane Center is also asking residents of the eastern Gulf Coast, including Florida, to monitor the storm closely since it has the potential to reach the US.
